[[!meta title="Office suite"]]

Tails includes <span class="application">[LibreOffice](http://www.libreoffice.org/)</span>,
a powerful office suite which embeds several tools:

  - **<span class="application">Writer</span>**, a word processor
  - **<span class="application">Calc</span>**, a spreasheet application
  - **<span class="application">Impress</span>**, a presentation engine
  - **<span class="application">Draw</span>**, a drawing and flowcharting
    application
  - **<span class="application">Math</span>**, for editing mathematics

To start <span class="application">LibreOffice</span> choose
<span class="menuchoice">
  <span class="guimenu">Applications</span>&nbsp;▸
  <span class="guisubmenu">Office</span>&nbsp;▸
  <span class="guimenuitem">LibreOffice</span></span>.

The <span class="application">LibreOffice</span> website provides complete [user
guides](https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Publications) for each
of these tools, translated into several languages.

